OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FInfected blood scandal:    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FFive facts we have learned 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A long-running public inquiry into what
OL,6, has been called the worst treatment    
OL,7, disaster in the history of the NHS will
OL,8, hear from its final witness on Friday. 
OL,10,FIt is thought tens of thousands were   
OL,11,Finfected with HIV and hepatitis between
OL,12,F1970 and 1991 after being given a      
OL,13,Fcontaminated drug or blood transfusion.
OL,15,FThe inquiry, which started in 2018, has
OL,16,Freviewed thousands of documents and    
OL,17,Fheard testimony from 370 witnesses.    
OL,19,FIt will publish its formal conclusions 
OL,20,Fand recommendations in the summer.     
